{"talk":{"id":19461,"name":"Gary Liu: The rapid growth of the Chinese internet -- and where it's headed","description":"The Chinese internet has grown at a staggering pace -- it now has more users than the combined populations of the US, UK, Russia, Germany, France and Canada. Even with its imperfections, the lives of once-forgotten populations have been irrevocably elevated because of it, says South China Morning Post CEO Gary Liu. In a fascinating talk, Liu details how the tech industry in China has developed -- from the innovative, like AI-optimized train travel, to the dystopian, like a social credit rating that both rewards and restricts citizens.","slug":"gary_liu_the_rapid_growth_of_the_chinese_internet_and_where_it_s_headed","recorded_at":"2018-04-10 00:00:00","published_at":"2018-07-09 14:54:29","updated_at":"2021-04-13 21:30:30","viewed_count":1583109,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":494,"name":"TED2018"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/eb8caad3451deddec65e97d43cbd05ff434bd22b_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/eb8caad3451deddec65e97d43cbd05ff434bd22b_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/eb8caad3451deddec65e97d43cbd05ff434bd22b_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/eb8caad3451deddec65e97d43cbd05ff434bd22b_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/909609add60259a1520750d9313cdce821e20b66_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GaryLiu_2018-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6274202,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GaryLiu_2018-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":17374380,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GaryLiu_2018-320k.mp4?api